OL,4,Cracist language upheld in MasterChef
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FIn a post on Instagram, Torode
OL,8,Fconfirmed he was the person alleged to
OL,9,Fhave used racist language but said he
OL,10,Fhad "no recollection of the incident"
OL,11,Fand was "shocked and saddened" by the
OL,12,Fallegation.
OL,14,FHis statement said: "Following
OL,15,Fpublication of the Executive Summary
OL,16,Fof the investigation into Gregg
OL,17,FWallace while working on MasterChef, I
OL,18,Fam aware of speculation that I am one
OL,19,Fof the two other individuals against
OL,20,Fwhom an allegation has been upheld.
