OL,7,F"For the sake of transparency, I
OL,8,Fconfirm that I am the individual who
OL,9,Fis alleged to have used racial
OL,10,Flanguage on one occasion. The
OL,11,Fallegation is that I did so sometime
OL,12,Fin 2018 or 2019, in a social
OL,13,Fsituation, and that the person I was
OL,14,Fspeaking with did not believe that it
OL,15,Fwas intended in a malicious way and
OL,16,Fthat I apologised immediately
OL,17,Fafterwards.
