OL,3,CJohn Torode says allegation of using
OL,4,Cracist language upheld in MasterChef
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FOn Monday, an investigation into the
OL,8,Fconduct of Gregg Wallace said more
OL,9,Fthan 40 allegations of inappropriate
OL,10,Fbehaviour were "found to be
OL,11,Fsubstantiated", including
OL,12,Finappropriate sexual language, being
OL,13,Fin a state of undress and one incident
OL,14,Fof "unwelcome physical contact".
OL,16,FWallace stepped back from presenting
OL,17,Fthe BBC show in November 2024 after
OL,18,Fseveral historical allegations were
OL,19,Fdisclosed.
